title: Week 10 Matchups + Double Wheel of Shame, OBJ Fallout - Fantasy Football Podcast for 11/12
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode to help you get a win in Week 10! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Week 10 matchup breakdowns, injury updates, and reactions to Odell Beckham joining the Rams! Plus, a recap of Thursday Night Football, and a double spin of the Wheel of Shame during the “Fantasy Faceoff” segment! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for November 12th, 2021.
  
 (02:40) - Thursday Night Recap
 (07:45) - FootClan Friday
 (08:40) - Thursday Night Recap continued
 (09:50) - NFL News
 (22:35) - Fantasy Forecast
 (23:05) - Buccaneers at Washington Football Team
 (28:00) - Panthers at Cardinals
 (34:05) - Vikings at Chargers
 (38:30) - Eagles at Broncos
 (44:55) - Seahawks at Packers
 (47:05) - Chiefs at Raiders
 (52:00) - Rams at 49ers
 (56:10) - Fantasy Faceoff + Wheel of Shame
